RedisRecord(working Title)
---

* some kind of database mapper for redis on rails
* uses ActiveModel to provide things like validations

Model
---

    require 'redisrecord'
    class MockModel < RedisRecord::Model
      def self.attrs
        [:body, :title]
      end
      attr_accessor *attrs
    end


Generator
---

    rails g redis model field1 field2

    rails g scaffold model field1:string field2:int -o redis


meta
